Reviewed-by: Hans de Goede <hdegoede@redhat.com>
Acked-by: Daniel Vetter <daniel.vetter@ffwll.ch>
Link: https://patchwork.freedesktop.org/patch/msgid/20201103113456.3066-2-tzimmermann@suse.de

